import React from "react";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import { Navbar, Nav, NavDropdown } from "react-bootstrap";

function Menu() {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg" className="mb-4"> {/* Adicione a classe 'mb-4' para ajustar o espaçamento */}
      <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Seu Logo Aqui</Navbar.Brand>
      <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
      <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
        <Nav>
          {/* Adicione o email do usuário aqui */}
          <NavDropdown title="example@example.com" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="16"
                height="16"
                fill="currentColor"
                className="bi bi-person-circle mr-1"
                viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              >
                {/* Conteúdo do ícone de perfil */}
              </svg>
              Perfil
            </NavDropdown.Item>
            <NavDropdown.Divider />
            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="16"
                height="16"
                fill="currentColor"
                className="bi bi-box-arrow-right mr-1"
                viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              >
                {/* Conteúdo do ícone de sair */}
              </svg>
              Sair
            </NavDropdown.Item>
          </NavDropdown>
        </Nav>
      </Navbar.Collapse>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default Menu;
